- Well, so much for my book.
[sighs]

22:03.523 --> 22:05.925
Or hanging out on a yacht.

22:10.096 --> 22:13.433
- You stood by me, Captain.

22:13.466 --> 22:16.069
You said my ideas were good.

22:16.102 --> 22:19.439
You're my number one hero.

22:19.472 --> 22:21.508
I know that's not a yacht,

22:21.541 --> 22:23.677
but I hope it counts
for something.

22:23.710 --> 22:25.178
<i>[dramatic music swells, ends]</i>

22:25.211 --> 22:26.513
- [exhales]

22:26.546 --> 22:27.647
See, Sarika?

22:27.681 --> 22:30.050
This is why Heather's
my favorite.

22:30.083 --> 22:32.752
Unless you have another aunt
in the publishing business?

22:32.786 --> 22:34.087
- No.
- Just the one?

22:34.120 --> 22:35.855
- Yeah.
